罗素·克劳将在尼克·凯夫被取消的《角斗士》续集中复活https://www.nme.com/news/film/russell-crowe-was-to-be-resurrected-in-nick-caves-cancelled-gladiator-sequel-3815457?ut m_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=罗素·克劳在尼克洞穴取消角斗士续集中复活Surej SinghMon, 25 Nov 2024 05:08:29 +0000 Film NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3815457 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/gladiator-russell-crowe@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/gladiator-russell-crowe@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/gladiator-russell-crowe@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/gladiator-russell-crowe@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/gladiator-russell-crowe@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/gladiator-russell-crowe@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/gladiator-russell-crowe@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>雷德利·斯科特聘请凯夫撰写剧本，其中包括传送门、罗马诸神和时间旅行</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/russell-crowe-was-to-be-resurrected-in-nick-caves-cancelled-gladiator-sequel-3815457">罗素·克劳将在尼克·凯夫取消的《角斗士》续集中复活，</a>这一消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/gladiator-russell-crowe@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/gladiator-russell-crowe@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/gladiator-russell-crowe@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/gladiator-russell-crowe@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/gladiator-russell-crowe@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/gladiator-russell-crowe@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/gladiator-russell-crowe@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>导演<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ridley-scott">雷德利·斯科特</a>透露，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/russell-crowe">罗素·克劳</a>原本打算在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nick-cave">尼克·凯夫</a>已取消的<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/gladiator-2"><em>《角斗士》</em></a>续集中继续扮演他的角色。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/gladiator-2-review-paul-mescal-3811514">《角斗士 2》评论：回到罗马观看保罗·梅斯卡尔的罗马斗兽场大小的续集</a></strong></li></ul><p>在 2000 年的史诗片中，克劳饰演马克西姆斯，一位罗马将军，后来成为勇敢的斗兽场战士，并在影片结尾去世。然而，根据雷德利·斯科特的说法，克罗希望回归拍摄计划中的续集，该续集当时由音乐家尼克·凯夫（Nick Cave）执笔。</p><p>斯科特向<a href="https://people.com/ridley-scott-says-russell-crowe-asked-to-be-in-gladiator-ii-exclusive-8748909" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《人物》杂志</em></a>回忆道：“大约 18 年前，拉塞尔和我就尝试过。我让尼克·凯夫写剧本，我一直对拉塞尔说，“但你死了。”他说：‘我知道我死了。我想死而复生。” </p><figure id="attachment_3810791" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3810791" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3810791" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/russell-crowe-joaquin-phoenix@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/russell-crowe-joaquin-phoenix@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/russell-crowe-joaquin-phoenix@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/russell-crowe-joaquin-phoenix@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/russell-crowe-joaquin-phoenix@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/russell-crowe-joaquin-phoenix@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/russell-crowe-joaquin-phoenix@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3810791" class="wp-caption-text">罗素·克劳和华金·菲尼克斯出席《角斗士》首映式。图片来源：Jeff Kravitz/FilmMagic, Inc</figcaption></figure><p>斯科特随后表示，凯夫复活克劳的马克西姆斯的解决方法是通过“门户”：“唯一的方法就是参加另一场战斗，通过一个垂死的战士，他回到战士的精神中。所以这就是他的门户。”</p><p>然而，据报道，克劳驳斥了这个想法，因为这意味着将由不同的演员来扮演复活版的马克西姆斯：“他说，‘所以这他妈的一点都不好，是吗？’这并没有真正发挥作用。”</p><p>根据<a href="https://www.bbc.com/culture/article/20180810-gladiator-2-was-written-and-its-mad" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>BBC</em> 2018 年的报道</a>，尼克·凯夫的<em>《角斗士 II》</em>将以马克西姆斯在来世的开场，在那里他遇到了几位堕落的罗马神灵。他们要求他杀死赫菲斯托斯神，作为回报，他可以与死去的妻子和儿子团聚。在他的旅程中的某个时刻，马克西姆斯在他去世大约二十年后被带回了生者的世界。 </p><figure id="attachment_3811316" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3811316" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3811316" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/bad_seeds_o2_3.jpg" alt="尼克·凯夫 (Nick Cave) 和 The Bad Seeds 于 2024 年 11 月在伦敦 O2 剧场演出。（摄影：Matthew Baker/Getty Images）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/bad_seeds_o2_3.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/bad_seeds_o2_3-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/bad_seeds_o2_3-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/bad_seeds_o2_3-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/bad_seeds_o2_3-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/bad_seeds_o2_3-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3811316" class="wp-caption-text">尼克·凯夫 (Nick Cave) 和 The Bad Seeds 于 2024 年 11 月在伦敦 O2 剧场演出。（摄影：Matthew Baker/Getty Images）</figcaption></figure><p>现在，在原作上映 23 年后， <em>《角斗士 II》</em>已经走向了不同的方向，由保罗·梅斯卡、丹泽尔·华盛顿和佩德罗·帕斯卡等人主演。在影片中，梅斯卡扮演 2000 年电影中的小男孩卢修斯。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/gladiator-2-review-paul-mescal-3811514">在一篇三星级评论中， <em>《NME》</em>将<em>《角斗士 II》</em>描述为第一部电影的“斗兽场大小的续集”</a> ，并补充道：“如果你喜欢<i>《角斗士》</i> ，那么你很可能也会喜欢这部电影。它有同样令人兴奋的部分——剑术、激动人心的演讲、令人讨厌的贵族得到了他们应得的。问题是这就是它给你的一切。你想要感觉自己正在看着马克西姆斯摘下头盔，再次第一次说出那段标志性的独白。</p><p> “你想要核心记忆被解锁的快感。您想知道在接下来的 10 年里您将在酒吧里向您的朋友引用麦斯卡尔酒的台词。 <i>《角斗士 2》</i>虽然虔诚地受到尊重，但只能提供对那段经历的褪色记忆。我有一个梦想，那就是罗马——这就是它。” </p><figure id="attachment_3811554" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3811554" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3811554" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Gladiator_2_Denzel_Washington.jpg" alt="角斗士" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Gladiator_2_Denzel_Washington.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Gladiator_2_Denzel_Washington-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Gladiator_2_Denzel_Washington-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Gladiator_2_Denzel_Washington-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Gladiator_2_Denzel_Washington-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Gladiator_2_Denzel_Washington-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3811554" class="wp-caption-text"> 《角斗士 2》中的丹泽尔·华盛顿。图片来源：派拉蒙影业</figcaption></figure><p>与此同时，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/gladiator-3-release-date-3812736">斯科特表示他正在考虑另一部续集</a>。他告诉法国<em>《Premiere</em> 》杂志：“不是认真的！我已经点燃了导火索<em>《角斗士 2》</em>的结局让人想起<em>《教父》</em>中迈克尔·柯里昂发现自己从事了一份他不想要的工作，并想知道，“现在，父亲，我该怎么办？”所以下一部[电影]将讲述一个不想呆在原地的人的故事。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/russell-crowe-was-to-be-resurrected-in-nick-caves-cancelled-gladiator-sequel-3815457">罗素·克劳将在尼克·凯夫取消的《角斗士》续集中复活，</a>这一消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
