ttachment_3767079" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3767079" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3767079" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/ghost-rite-here-rite-now@2000x1270.jpg" alt="托比亚斯·福吉 (Tobias Forge) 饰演幽灵主唱 Papa Emeritus IV" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/ghost-rite-here-rite-now@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/ghost-rite-here-rite-now@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/ghost-rite-here-rite-now@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/ghost-rite-here-rite-now@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/ghost-rite-here-rite-now@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/ghost-rite-here-rite-now@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3767079" class="wp-caption-text">鬼。图片来源：Ryan Chang/Trafalgar Release</figcaption></figure><p> <em>NME</em>在对<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/ghost-rite-here-rite-now-movie-3766873"><em>《Rite Here Right Now》</em>的四星评论</a>中写道：“如果您是一名普通粉丝， <em>《Rite Here Rite Now》</em>将为您带来有趣、愉快的体验，让您在他们的下一张专辑或巡演之前顺利度过。但如果你是一个顽固分子，那么这是必不可少的观看内容 - 不仅是因为它令人兴奋的现场时刻，而且是为了扣人心弦的幽灵传奇的下一部分。”</p><p> Ghost 还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ghost-announce-2025-world-tour-with-shows-in-the-uk-europe-us-and-north-america-buy-tickets-3807064">宣布将于 2025 年进行世界巡演</a>，包括在英国、欧洲和北美进行演出。美国日期的门票<a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Fghost-tickets%2Fartist%2F1878819" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里出售</a>，英国的门票<a href="https://www.ticketmaster.co.uk/search?q=Ghost" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里出售</a>，欧洲的球迷可以<a style="font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;" href="https://ghost-official.com/#tour" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里购买门票</a>，最后，<a href="https://ghost-official.com/#tour">墨西哥的球迷可以在这里购买门票</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ghost-announce-new-comic-book-series-co-written-by-frontman-3815443">《Ghost》后宣布由主唱共同创作的新漫画系列</a>首先在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上出现。</p> ;
